data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF that will be completed before closing. Saltwater POOL home on the 8th hole in Scenic Hills Country Club. New high efficiency pool pump, and salt cell, added in 2023. Kitchen has been remodeled with level 3 granite countertops, soft close custom cabinetry and newer Samsung smart appliances. Second floor has 2 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, one with a jetted tub.  The large second floor primary suite has a deck with a great view of the pool and golf course. Lower level has a bedroom and full bath.  The lower level also has a family room, fireplace and wet bar that makes it the perfect place for hosting guests!  The lower level would also make a great in-law suite with its own entrance.  There is a RV parking spot with 50 amp hookup.  This home has newer double pane vinyl windows.  The siding was recently replaced and painted.  There is an oversized garage with plenty of storage room, shelves, and cabinetry.  This home is on a dead end within walking distance to the Scenic Hills Country Club Restaurant and Bar and the UWF hiking and biking trails.  No new homes can be built on the surrounding wooded areas near this home as they have been zoned as a conservation!  This home has a view of a whimsical wooded area from the front porch and a view of the golf course from of the backyard.
